movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: UNDERATED
review: I cannot tell you how many times I've watched this movie, i would restart it as soon as it finishes. This movie is the definition of Star Wars. The planets, the scrip, characters & aliens are so unique. The story is amazing but for many hard to understand. Almost everything from this movie is iconic. The scenery and aesthetic of it is one of the best from all the episodes. A great start to the saga !
